# Claude Code / ACDM dev-support — local only, kept out of the public artifact (B7),
# EXCEPT the repo-policy rules below: they describe the repo / are read by repo-tooling
# and must travel with a clone (ADR-015 "protection travels with the repo"). B7 refined
# to a process/policy cut — dev-tooling stays out, repo-policy travels.
.claude/*
!.claude/rules/
.claude/rules/*
!.claude/rules/data-protection.md
!.claude/rules/internal-docs-boundary.md
!.claude/rules/publish-readiness.md

# Local MCP server config (contains absolute paths)
.mcp.json

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# Test coverage
coverage/

